Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe that this is the future that awaits me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me. The Organization's interfering with events again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying it's all the choice of Steins;Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when it all began, two weeks ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I have missed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you again if I survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:01:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,El. Psy. Congroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,435)\bord0\shad0}Two weeks ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that Hawaiian style, Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not Hawaiian. It's LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,LA?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He mentioned it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Faris was invited to participate in a Rai-Net battle in America, so she invited us along.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, the federal government wants the power of the great Hououin Kyouma on its side!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wild delusions, fail as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's a message from Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She says that the research she's working on is almost done, so she can come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like she wants you to come too, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:02:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Okabe doesn't have to come though. It's not like I want to see him or anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a true tsundere. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Future Gadget Laboratory could definitely use a foothold for global expansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin's a tsundere too, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,America? Don't bother coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me something back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like, Moeka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:35.42,Sign1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB5ADB0&\frx4\fry2\frz17.585\pos(696,51)\fax.05}From: {\c&HFDFFFF&}Shin{ing Fingers}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:32.59,Sign1,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\frx2\fry0\frz18.993\pos(798,94)\fax.05}Macadamia \Nnuts x6
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.42,Sign1,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs30\frz19.571\t(0,700,\frz17.526)\fax.05\clip(m 502 672 l 1028 477 838 13 332 176)\move(901,517,734,54,0,700)}...anything but that.\NMoeka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Some sweets would be sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, I would need to keep this secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am mad scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,United States. Chaos and invade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mad scientist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a small citizen. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kyouma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To think the Organization would join forces with the federal government in a bid to stop me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you haven't changed, Okabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I thought it was my \Nexperiment-loving assistant, Cristina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you may have been an agent of the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a walking failure. I have to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wild delusions, fail as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit blabbering. Let's get going already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rukako...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go call a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so out of breath?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For the taxi fare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:04:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Faris!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you cancel the hotel I booked?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't let the Organization know about our plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, is it the Seven Kings of North America?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The Seven's Philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A Japan vs. America battle already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But we must avoid pointless conflicts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I must, I will use the secret Desert Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me you've already mastered it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come! A distant 8770 kilometers from home, I announce it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Until my body breaks and my soul passes on to Valhalla,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall fight valiantly in the Ragnarok!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you have quite the nice room for an assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys can stay here until you find somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just do as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just drink what you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've seen this scene before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This really is the most relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how much do you love labs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How's life over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't end up writing any \Npapers on time machines, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you mentioned something before about a different world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems there might be others who have\N memories of other world lines, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:07:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I only remember you saving me at the radio building, and then trying to find you to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's all you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you found something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a motel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to just leave us here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got no choice. With your budget, motels are the only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Motels are where aliens take over people's bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're where hockey-masked lunatics butcher people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't confuse reality and fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that you see those kind of things in the movies, but it's still scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be too much for Mayuri and Urushibara alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be fine staying with Okarin. We used to sleep together often when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you imagining?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear her say it was when we were kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, the girls and guys shouldn't share a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Urushibara—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a guy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I'll stay here with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe and Hashida are together. I'll stay with Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? I have to stay all by myself? It's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Hashida can stay alone, and I'll stay with Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That leaves Okabe and—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind, if it's with Kyouma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, he's a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in the end, Makise ended up alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no problem with Rukako and Mayuri staying together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lesbianism is in the air. Ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it's lesbian in the other room, then this room is—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's decide with rock-paper-scissors which one of us sleeps in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I let him have my sleeping place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Supah Hakah is my important right-hand man, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you lost in rock-paper-scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are you still up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you come in? Just for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you about a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is Diet Dr Pepper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring some home as souvenirs. \NWith the current exchange rate, it's cheaper here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it about the Organization? Or perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to joke, just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard you say that before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Another story, another world line. Don't mind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to ask about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm not all that sure about your theory of world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But just as you said, I've dreamed of things I haven't experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, I had a dream where I was trying to cheer you up on a bridge in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've dreamed about using the whiteboard while trying hard to explain something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've dreamed about fixing your lab coat in some dark place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as I thought. You still have some of your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So those were real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether they're real or not is hard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They may as well be dreams to you in this world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But they really happened in some other world lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I have another question...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I had another... weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One where you and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need to go to the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin and Kurisu sure do get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This decides it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a virus card! Faris wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Faris! Faris! Faris!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:13:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A male beauty on stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the "Nyan Nyan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Assistant, you're supposed to be a Japanese maid in America spreading our glorious culture!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember anyone saying anything about that! \NAnd I don't want to do that either!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We agreed to work here to pay for the plane tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural for a lab member to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recall having someone else pay for my ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lab members are one soul, one body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you do it too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have so much energy,\N I guess you slept well last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like something was bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just a bit curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not really it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good can come out of \Nremembering other world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd planned to forget it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Suzuha here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The last thing she said to me was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Thank you. I'll see you in seven years."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The time machine hasn't been invented in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She can't exist here until she's born in seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is there a time machine in this world line too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's true, it may mean World War III.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Okabe is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed to be in a panic,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I saw him go outside and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just heard that someone looking like him got in a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I wonder if something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you followed me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you aren't her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I just entered the Rai-Net tournament and am going to Las Vegas with my friends who live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But, for you to follow me all the way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,she must be really important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl I look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know where she is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'll see her again in seven years. Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite the wonderful story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A fortune teller told me that I'll get \Nmarried and have a kid in seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for taking up your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seven years from now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she wouldn't know what I was talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,$0.67 left. The battery's dead too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to get back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That was how it all started, two hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I can't let it end here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the mad scientist, Hououin Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't even been able to tell her properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,An illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the reality as your brain interprets it \Nfrom the signals sent through your retinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to come searching for me, \Nthen at least check the gas before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your phone battery's dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a total of 67 cents,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and you were about to die lying face down in the middle of the highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear it from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had seen an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,An old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't anything I needed to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'd forget it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act like it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very important to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Important?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said... It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how I said I had another weird dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too realistic to be just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, it's real. To me, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that I loved you in another world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have spent a lot of time together in another world line,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but those times are all dreams to me in this world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So... it's very confusing for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I possess the Reading Steiner, so I remember everything from the other world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The three weeks I spent with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was a much, much longer time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know because I was with you all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In any world line, any time, any place, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Makise Kurisu, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here and now, how do you feel about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.76,0:22:10.43,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}The billions of heartbeats that pulse around the globe
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.43,0:22:17.10,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}are naught but a trivial matter to you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.10,0:22:22.32,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}Although I'm caught in the past and I bewail the future
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.32,0:22:28.24,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I cannot forgive an error of any size
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.24,0:22:34.33,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}Both our infinite dreams and our sketched out future
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.33,0:22:40.13,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}are naught but theories of arrogance granted to us
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.13,0:22:46.30,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}The finite is indicated by two hands of a clock
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.30,0:22:50.68,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}As I inch ever closer towards the cruelly contracted choice
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.68,0:22:52.89,op trans,,0,0,0,,Hacking to the gate
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.35,0:23:00.23,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}That drives my will to go beyond the World Lines
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.23,0:23:05.24,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}in order to preserve that smile of yours
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.24,0:23:12.16,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}Once more, into a temporal loop devoid of sorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.16,0:23:18.42,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I'm drawn in, a solitary observer
Dialogue: 1,0:23:58.91,0:24:05.79,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}That drives my will to go beyond the World Lines
Dialogue: 1,0:24:05.79,0:24:10.80,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}in order to preserve that smile of yours
